The Nigerian Army on Friday announced that the online application for Direct Short Service Commission Course has commenced. A statement on the official Twitter handle of the Nigerian Army made this known on Friday. It said the application starts 25 March & ends 6 May 2022. “PUBLIC ANNOUNCEMENT “This is to inform the general public that the online application for Direct Short Service Commission Course 26/2022 has commenced. Application starts 25 March & ends 6 May 2022. “Visit recruitment.army.mil.ng. Application is Free, Beware of Internet Fraudsters.”